\v 20 <a name="02002102000014" ll="SDBH:חָכָם, קסם:000000">智慧人</a>​的​<a name="02002102000012" ll="SDBH:נָוֶה:000001">居所</a>​<a name="02002102000002" ll="SDBH:אֹוצָר:000000">积蓄</a>​<a name="02002102000004" ll="SDBH:חמד:000001">宝物</a>​与​<a name="02002102000008" ll="SDBH:שֶׁמֶן:000000" il="Italian_olive_oil_2007;NBGbs20100214-0211;il_oil_press_d01" tl="HOTTP2769">膏油</a>​；​<a name="02002102000018" ll="SDBH:כְּסִיל:000000">愚昧人</a>​却​<a name="02002102000022" ll="SDBH:בלע:000000">挥霍一空</a>​。
    
