\v 11 <a name="02002601100012" ll="SDBH:כְּסִיל:000000">愚昧人</a>​<a name="02002601100014" ll="SDBH:שׁנה:000007">重复</a>​做​<a name="02002601100018" ll="SDBH:אִוֶּלֶת:000000">愚昧</a>​<a name="02002601100018" ll="SDBH:אִוֶּלֶת:000000">之</a>​<a name="02002601100018" ll="SDBH:אִוֶּלֶת:000000">事</a>​，​就如​<a name="02002601100004" ll="SDBH:כֶּלֶב:000000">狗</a>​<a name="02002601100006" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000023">转</a>​<a name="02002601100006" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000023">过来</a>​吃​自己​<a name="02002601100010" ll="SDBH:קֵא:000000">所</a>​<a name="02002601100010" ll="SDBH:קֵא:000000">吐</a>​<a name="02002601100010" ll="SDBH:קֵא:000000">的</a>​。
    
